{
  "newspaper_id": "lankadeepa-lk",
  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/news/\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbb-\u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca-\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0-\u0d85\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dba-\u0dba\u0ddd\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf-\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u0db8\u0d9a-\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1-\u0db6\u0dd1/101-619022",
  "time_ut": 1661859651,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbb \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0 \u0d85\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dba \u0dba\u0ddd\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u0db8\u0d9a \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Budget proposals cannot be implemented without a stable government",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Harini Amarasuriya, Member of Parliament of National People's Party, said that budget proposals cannot be implemented without a stable government.",
        "The government is now changing the decisions made six months ago. There should be a stable government to implement the proposals. This is a government that has set up. The government's budget speech has received cold responses.",
        "The economic crisis is mainly affected by the absence of a stable government. The usual things presented by the previous government have been presented this time as well.",
        "Much attention has been given to education. The opportunity has been created for foreign students to come and study in Sri Lanka. We are not against that. Before providing facilities to foreign students, necessary facilities should be provided to the students of this country."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [
          {
